      <title>套利交易最喜爱的墨西哥比索因中东风险上升而受到打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/carry-trade-favorite-mexican-peso-smacked-by-rising-mideast-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥比索跌幅四年来最大，原因是中东冲突加剧削弱了对墨西哥比索的需求，而墨西哥比索一直是套利交易最喜欢的目标之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/carry-trade-favorite-mexican-peso-smacked-by-rising-mideast-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 05:52:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
